{"arkId":"cl010482635","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010482635","modified ":"2025-10-04","title":"Tasse du d\u00e9jeuner des Portraits de la famille royale et des Vues de Neuilly : Cl\u00e9mentine d\u2019Orl\u00e9ans (1817-1907)","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tasse du d\u00e9jeuner des Portraits de la famille royale et des Vues de Neuilly : Cl\u00e9mentine d\u2019Orl\u00e9ans (1817-1907)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis-Philippe (1830-1848) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine-\u003EMonarchie de Juillet (1830-1848)-\u003Emaison d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1835 - 1837","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 562 - Marie d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans, Acc\u00e8s r\u00e9serv\u00e9","room":"Salle 562, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1835,"endYear":1837,"imprecision":"","text":"1\u00e8re moiti\u00e9 du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Barre, Jean Jacques","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","dates":[{"date":"03\/08\/1793","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"10\/06\/1855","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Graveur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q1751153"},{"label":"Moriot, Nicolas-Marie","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Peintre sur c\u00e9ramique","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Manufacture de S\u00e8vres","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q653307"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"RFML.OA.2021.12.2","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"tasse ; art de la table","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"L\u2019id\u00e9e de ce d\u00e9jeuner appara\u00eet en 1834 et le travail commence au d\u00e9but de l\u2019ann\u00e9e 1835. Il est pr\u00e9vu d\u2019orner les trois grandes pi\u00e8ces de forme des portraits du roi, de la reine et de Madame Ad\u00e9la\u00efde, les tasses d\u2019un portrait de chacun des enfants de Louis-Philippe et Marie-Am\u00e9lie, d\u2019o\u00f9 leur nombre inhabituel de huit, et enfin les soucoupes de vues de Neuilly.\r\nLe d\u00e9jeuner entre en magasin le 1er avril 1837. Il est appel\u00e9 D\u00e9jeuner des Portraits de la famille royale et des Vues de Neuilly. Le d\u00e9jeuner est livr\u00e9 \u00e0 la reine Marie-Am\u00e9lie, \u00e0 la suite d\u2019une visite \u00e0 la manufacture de la famille royale alors en s\u00e9jour \u00e0 Saint-Cloud, le 22 ao\u00fbt 1837 pour la somme importante de 5995 francs, ce qui en fait l\u2019un des d\u00e9jeuners les plus chers livr\u00e9s \u00e0 la famille royale sous la monarchie de Juillet. \r\nLes portraits sont peints \u00e0 la mani\u00e8re de cam\u00e9e par Nicolas-Marie Moriot (Versailles, 1788-1856), peintre miniaturiste, actif \u00e0 S\u00e8vres de 1828 et 1848. Moriot utilise les portraits ex\u00e9cut\u00e9s en 1832 par Jean-Jacques Barre (1793-1855), graveur g\u00e9n\u00e9ral de la Monnaie, diffus\u00e9s en pl\u00e2tre (mus\u00e9e du Louvre), ou \u00e9dit\u00e9s \u00e0 S\u00e8vres en biscuit. Il s\u2019agit ici la princesse Cl\u00e9mentine (M[arie]. Cl\u00e9m[entine]. Car[oline]. L\u00e9op[oldine]. Clot[hilde]). Cl\u00e9mentine est peinte par Moriot en janvier 1836, retouch\u00e9e en mars.\r\nLe d\u00e9cor ornemental, d\u2019un grand raffinement, est con\u00e7u par Charles Leloy (1774-1846) sur un \u00ab fond de moufle brun viol\u00e2tre d\u00e9cor colori\u00e9 \u00e0 la mani\u00e8re d\u2019Herculanum \u00bb. Certains dessins pour le d\u00e9jeuner de cet ornemaniste prolifique sont conserv\u00e9s dans les archives de la manufacture de S\u00e8vres. Au revers de chaque tasse, un enfant est assis sur des ornements dor\u00e9s dans un encadrement v\u00e9g\u00e9tal, \u00e0 chaque fois diff\u00e9rent : ici du jasmin pour la princesse Cl\u00e9mentine.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"12,1","displayDimension":"12,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"9,3","displayDimension":"9,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"11,8","displayDimension":"11,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : porcelaine dure","placeOfCreation":"S\u00e8vres (Ile-de-France = Ile de France-\u003EHauts-de-Seine = Hauts de Seine)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Mandataire : Galerie Dragesco-Cramoisan, Paris\r\nacquis avec la tasse num\u00e9rot\u00e9e RFML.OA.2021.12.2","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date d\u0027affectation","value":"12\/05\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de commission des acquisitions","value":"12\/05\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de d\u00e9cision","value":"12\/05\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"date de l\u0027inscription sur l\u0027inventaire","value":"12\/05\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021},{"type":"Commission acquisition","value":"12\/05\/2021","startYear":2021,"endYear":2021}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"period":[{"value":"Louis-Philippe (1830-1848)"}],"place":[{"value":"S\u00e8vres"}],"objectType":[{"value":"art de la table"},{"value":"tasse"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[{"objectUrl":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010482634","type":"Ensemble"}],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105131_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105131_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2021 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105133_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105133_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2021 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"","position":1},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105134_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105134_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2021 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"","position":2},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105135_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105135_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2021 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"","position":3},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105138_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000482635\/0001105138_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2021 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Lou